Name: Average resolution time following 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' across all cases
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E8EF99C100> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration difference between 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' before transitioning to any 'Accepted + In Progress' state
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Shortest time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Closed' across variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average delay introduced by 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in resolving incidents compared to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total cumulative time of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average lead time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Resolved' in incidents with high impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest time gap between 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and any 'Accepted + Assigned' activity
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Shortest time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Closed' excluding weekends
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Closed'
